915
01:06:44,177 --> 01:06:48,677
何より強い 命の息吹
A breath of life stronger than anything

916
01:06:49,177 --> 01:06:53,177
運命巡って 奇跡になるから
Fate goes around and becomes a miracle

917
01:06:53,677 --> 01:06:59,177
隣で 綴ってあげる
I'll write it down by your side

918
01:06:59,677 --> 01:07:03,677
小さな 幸せが募る
Small happiness accumulates

919
01:07:04,177 --> 01:07:10,177
みんなへ
To everyone

920
01:07:10,677 --> 01:07:18,677
奇跡のような 君と作るメモリ
Like a miracle, the memories I make with you

921
01:07:35,477 --> 01:07:38,477
はい！というわけで、
