And finally, there are announcements from the fan club...

1005
01:12:40,589 --> 01:12:43,189
4つございますので、そちらもぜひ聞いてください。
...four of them, so please listen to them too.

1006
01:12:43,189 --> 01:12:46,489
1つ目。なんと、ときのそらオフィシャルファンクラブが...
First. Believe it or not, the Tokino Sora Official Fan Club...

1007
01:12:46,489 --> 01:12:49,189
来週で1周年を迎えます！
...will celebrate its 1st anniversary next week!

1008
01:12:49,189 --> 01:12:52,089
